      • ReportClient

        public ReportClient(java.lang.String appKey,
            java.lang.String masterSecret,
            HttpProxy proxy,
            JMessageConfig config)
        Create a JMessage Base Client
        参数:
        appKey - The KEY of one application on JPush.
        masterSecret - API access secret of the appKey.
        proxy - The proxy, if there is no proxy, should be null.
        config - The client configuration. Can use JMessageConfig.getInstance() as default.

    • 方法详细资料

      • v2GetMessageList

        public MessageListResult v2GetMessageList(int count,
                                 java.lang.String begin_time,
                                 java.lang.String end_time)
                                   throws APIConnectionException,
                                          APIRequestException
        Get message list from history, messages will store 60 days.
        参数:
        count - Necessary parameter. The count of the message list.
        begin_time - Necessary parameter. The format must follow by 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss'
        end_time - Necessary parameter. The format must follow by 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss'
        返回:
        MessageListResult
        抛出:
        APIConnectionException - connect exception
        APIRequestException - request exception

      • v2GetMessageListByCursor

        public MessageListResult v2GetMessageListByCursor(java.lang.String cursor)
                                           throws APIConnectionException,
                                                  APIRequestException
        Get message list with cursor, the cursor will effective in 120 seconds. And will return same count of messages as first request.
        参数:
        cursor - First request will return cursor
        返回:
        MessageListResult
        抛出:
        APIConnectionException - connect exception
        APIRequestException - request exception

      • v2GetUserMessages

        public MessageListResult v2GetUserMessages(java.lang.String username,
                                  int count,
                                  java.lang.String begin_time,
                                  java.lang.String end_time)
                                    throws APIConnectionException,
                                           APIRequestException
        Get message list from user's record, messages will store 60 days.
        参数:
        username - Necessary parameter.
        count - Necessary parameter. The count of the message list.
        begin_time - Optional parameter. The format must follow by 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss'
        end_time - Optional parameter. The format must follow by 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss'
        返回:
        MessageListResult
        抛出:
        APIConnectionException - connect exception
        APIRequestException - request exception

      • getMessageStatistic

        public MessageStatListResult getMessageStatistic(java.lang.String timeUnit,
                                        java.lang.String start,
                                        int duration)
                                          throws APIConnectionException,
                                                 APIRequestException
        Get message statistic. Detail instructions please refer to https://docs.jiguang.cn/jmessage/server/rest_api_im_report_v2/#_6
        参数:
        timeUnit - MUST be one of HOUR, DAY, MONTH
        start - start time, when timeUnit is HOUR, format: yyyy-MM-dd HH,
        duration - depends on timeUnit, the duration has limit
        返回:
        MessageStatListResult
        抛出:
        APIConnectionException - connect exception
        APIRequestException - request exception
